                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1112-18430403 t18430403-1112-punishment-8"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">WEATHERLY</hi>,—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18430403-1112-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18430403-1112-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-1112-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 31.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy.—
